articles.title: GOP candidates gear up one month before Iowa caucuses
articles.description: Former President Donald Trump extended his considerable lead in Iowa this week, according to a new poll. The state is holding the first Republican caucus in just one month. CBS News politics reporter Zak Hudak has the latest analysis.
